"Im not entirely sure why their running, although I do think Cliffjumper
is just going to blow off some steam. He's a scrapper, and I dont know
how he manages to keep calm out of battle. Beachcomber on the other hand
dosent get mad, but he is good friends with Jumper, so he's probably
just going to make sure nothing happens" Firedrill said, with warmth in
his voice.
